WEBVTT

02:33:03.251 --> 02:33:05.501
Where are your parents from?

02:33:05.751 --> 02:33:07.043
North India.

02:33:07.334 --> 02:33:09.126
Where is your husband from?

02:33:09.376 --> 02:33:10.834
South India.

02:33:10.918 --> 02:33:12.001
Did you hear that, scoundrel?

02:33:13.293 --> 02:33:15.501
We are there and here as well.

02:33:15.709 --> 02:33:18.834
We stay apart, but we stay together.

02:33:19.668 --> 02:33:21.251
India is unique.

02:33:22.668 --> 02:33:27.334
If you try to tear us apart,
I'll tear you apart, scoundrel.

02:33:29.209 --> 02:33:31.209
Hey, I am Big Bull, you scoundrel!
